episodes.title: I didn't realise I was in a cult
episodes.description:
@babygurllans 
I'm Allanah Freddi. 
BA in Psychology @ UniMelb. 
In today’s vlog, how I found out I was in a cult. I will be sharing the true story of the time that I didn't know I was in a cult because I was the maddest one there. I will be discussing what kundalini yoga is, how it works, as well as how I escaped the kundalini yoga cult. I will tell you exactly how God got me home from this cult, and then I will speak a bit on the importance of faith.
 ––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––
